    "1c83b07c-81ff-8056-88e5-ca2c9a013cbf": {
      "value": {
        "id": "1c83b07c-81ff-8056-88e5-ca2c9a013cbf",
        "type": "text",
        "properties": {
          "title": [
            [
              "YouTubeにストーリーをアップロードしているので、ゲームに興味はないけどストーリーを読みたい方は、"
            ],
            [
              "こちら",
              [
                [
                  "a",
                  "https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLkVIYO-uZg45fthqFM29tRF4lOMXAkaPM"
                ]
              ]
            ],
            [
              "から読んでみてください。"
            ]
          ]
        },
        "parent_id": "1c83b07c-81ff-8013-861e-e033d11cfdb9",
        "parent_table": "block",
        "created_time": 1743508707589,
        "last_edited_time": 1759941067633
      }
    },
    "2863b07c-81ff-8080-9d16-d607cb683462": {
      "value": {
        "id": "2863b07c-81ff-8080-9d16-d607cb683462",
        "type": "text",
        "properties": {
          "title": [
            [
              "自分でゲームをインストールしてプレイしたい方へ："
            ]
          ]
        },
        "parent_id": "1c83b07c-81ff-8013-861e-e033d11cfdb9",
        "parent_table": "block",
        "created_time": 1759939174767,
        "last_edited_time": 1759939197305
      }
    },
    "1c83b07c-81ff-80f9-b15a-eefa202a2efd": {
      "value": {
        "id": "1c83b07c-81ff-80f9-b15a-eefa202a2efd",
        "type": "text",
        "properties": {
          "title": [
            [
              "崩壊学園のメインストーリーは主に（追想編）、新生編、崩壊学園編の３つがあり、今から崩壊学園を始める人には崩壊学園編から始めることをオススメします。理由としては"
            ]
          ]
        },
        "parent_id": "1c83b07c-81ff-8013-861e-e033d11cfdb9",
        "parent_table": "block",
        "created_time": 1743505132120,
        "last_edited_time": 1745697053051
      }
    },
    "1c83b07c-81ff-80aa-b97f-eea303b1243c": {
      "value": {
        "id": "1c83b07c-81ff-80aa-b97f-eea303b1243c",
        "type": "bulleted_list",
        "properties": {
          "title": [
            [
              "キアナ達の物語は新生編にて一旦完結しています。崩壊学園編はその後の世界の物語（崩壊3rdの第二部に近い）であり、これまでとは別のライター様が担当されています。なので、ここから始めてもほとんどの内容は問題なく理解できます。"
            ]
          ]
        },
        "parent_id": "1c83b07c-81ff-8013-861e-e033d11cfdb9",
        "parent_table": "block",
        "created_time": 1743505451037,
        "last_edited_time": 1759939231992
      }
    },
    "1c83b07c-81ff-80f8-ab38-f78920627ad7": {
      "value": {
        "id": "1c83b07c-81ff-80f8-ab38-f78920627ad7",
        "type": "bulleted_list",
        "properties": {
          "title": [
            [
              "追想編、新生編は現在では読めなくなっている物語も多く、また順番も整理されていないのでかなり読みにくいです。そしてすごく長いです。"
            ]
          ]
        },
        "parent_id": "1c83b07c-81ff-8013-861e-e033d11cfdb9",
        "parent_table": "block",
        "created_time": 1743505474234,
        "last_edited_time": 1759939292303
      }
    },
    "1c83b07c-81ff-8071-8c1a-d1b324981c6c": {
      "value": {
        "id": "1c83b07c-81ff-8071-8c1a-d1b324981c6c",
        "type": "bulleted_list",
        "properties": {
          "title": [
            [
              "崩壊学園編は個人的には超超超面白いです。"
            ]
          ]
        },
        "parent_id": "1c83b07c-81ff-8013-861e-e033d11cfdb9",
        "parent_table": "block",
        "created_time": 1743505632627,
        "last_edited_time": 1743505744775
      }
    },
    "1c83b07c-81ff-8079-bf14-f274b3a882be": {
      "value": {
        "id": "1c83b07c-81ff-8079-bf14-f274b3a882be",
        "type": "text",
        "properties": {
          "title": [
            [
              "そのため、まずは崩壊学園編から始めてみて、興味を持ったら過去の物語も読んでみるのがよいと思います。（少なくとも「街燃の詩」までは進めることをオススメします。）"
            ]
          ]
        },
        "parent_id": "1c83b07c-81ff-8013-861e-e033d11cfdb9",
        "parent_table": "block",
        "created_time": 1743505638883,
        "last_edited_time": 1754585470159
      }
    },
    "1ca3b07c-81ff-807a-9c0d-dbe6ce6aee4f": {
      "value": {
        "id": "1ca3b07c-81ff-807a-9c0d-dbe6ce6aee4f",
        "type": "sub_sub_header",
        "properties": {
          "title": [
            [
              "どれを読むか"
            ]
          ]
        },
        "parent_id": "1c83b07c-81ff-8013-861e-e033d11cfdb9",
        "parent_table": "block",
        "created_time": 1743693455064,
        "last_edited_time": 1743694097001
      }
    },
    "3173b07c-81ff-80c7-ba56-db93933776b0": {
      "value": {
        "id": "3173b07c-81ff-80c7-ba56-db93933776b0",
        "type": "divider",
        "parent_id": "1c83b07c-81ff-8013-861e-e033d11cfdb9",
        "parent_table": "block",
        "created_time": 1772473265278,
        "last_edited_time": 1772473265924
      }
    },
    "1c83b07c-81ff-80e7-abcc-e1b0298ef9aa": {
      "value": {
        "id": "1c83b07c-81ff-80e7-abcc-e1b0298ef9aa",
        "type": "text",
        "properties": {
          "title": [
            [
              "崩壊学園編の物語にはメイン、サブ、限定の3種類があります。"
            ]
          ]
        },
        "parent_id": "1c83b07c-81ff-8013-861e-e033d11cfdb9",
        "parent_table": "block",
        "created_time": 1743508068059,
        "last_edited_time": 1759939322156
      }
    },
    "1ca3b07c-81ff-8035-bc88-d6048b9b4fae": {
      "value": {
        "id": "1ca3b07c-81ff-8035-bc88-d6048b9b4fae",
        "type": "text",
        "properties": {
          "title": [
            [
              "メインは本編であり、全部重要です。"
            ]
          ]
        },
        "parent_id": "1c83b07c-81ff-8013-861e-e033d11cfdb9",
        "parent_table": "block",
        "created_time": 1743693581689,
        "last_edited_time": 1745697156019
      }
    },
    "1ca3b07c-81ff-80bf-b081-f10cc6bfa1a9": {
      "value": {
        "id": "1ca3b07c-81ff-80bf-b081-f10cc6bfa1a9",
        "type": "text",
        "properties": {
          "title": [
            [
              "サブは読んでいなくてもメインの内容の7割程度は理解できるようになっていますが、物語の背景などを知るには読んでおくべきです。"
            ]
          ]
        },
        "parent_id": "1c83b07c-81ff-8013-861e-e033d11cfdb9",
        "parent_table": "block",
        "created_time": 1743693580063,
        "last_edited_time": 1745697197318
      }
    },
    "1c83b07c-81ff-807a-a7d5-d98a720d226b": {
      "value": {
        "id": "1c83b07c-81ff-807a-a7d5-d98a720d226b",
        "type": "text",
        "properties": {
          "title": [
            [
              "限定は日常系であり読まなくても支障はほぼありませんが、物語が好きな方はぜひ読んでみてください。"
            ]
          ]
        },
        "parent_id": "1c83b07c-81ff-8013-861e-e033d11cfdb9",
        "parent_table": "block",
        "created_time": 1743508117612,
        "last_edited_time": 1759939326748
      }
    },
    "1ca3b07c-81ff-801d-bb33-faeb1ad9a94e": {
      "value": {
        "id": "1ca3b07c-81ff-801d-bb33-faeb1ad9a94e",
        "type": "bulleted_list",
        "properties": {
          "title": [
            [
              "とりあえずどんな感じなのか知りたい方はメインのみ"
            ]
          ]
        },
        "parent_id": "1c83b07c-81ff-8013-861e-e033d11cfdb9",
        "parent_table": "block",
        "created_time": 1743693996153,
        "last_edited_time": 1743694023107
      }
    },
    "1ca3b07c-81ff-8025-a1c4-e4f18037cdd2": {
      "value": {
        "id": "1ca3b07c-81ff-8025-a1c4-e4f18037cdd2",
        "type": "bulleted_list",
        "properties": {
          "title": [
            [
              "普通に読みたい人はメインとサブ"
            ]
          ]
        },
        "parent_id": "1c83b07c-81ff-8013-861e-e033d11cfdb9",
        "parent_table": "block",
        "created_time": 1743694040599,
        "last_edited_time": 1743694080165
      }
    },
    "1ca3b07c-81ff-8093-bc59-df89656edc73": {
      "value": {
        "id": "1ca3b07c-81ff-8093-bc59-df89656edc73",
        "type": "bulleted_list",
        "properties": {
          "title": [
            [
              "じっくりと細部まで理解したい方は全て"
            ]
          ]
        },
        "parent_id": "1c83b07c-81ff-8013-861e-e033d11cfdb9",
        "parent_table": "block",
        "created_time": 1743694080162,
        "last_edited_time": 1743694084152
      }
    },
    "1ca3b07c-81ff-8009-bebb-e0ff4a31a94e": {
      "value": {
        "id": "1ca3b07c-81ff-8009-bebb-e0ff4a31a94e",
        "type": "text",
        "properties": {
          "title": [
            [
              "という感じで読むのがオススメです。"
            ]
          ]
        },
        "parent_id": "1c83b07c-81ff-8013-861e-e033d11cfdb9",
        "parent_table": "block",
        "created_time": 1743694114744,
        "last_edited_time": 1743694123189
      }
    },
    "1c83b07c-81ff-8091-9acc-f9531dac1c00": {
      "value": {
